{"word":"μελεδαίνω","slug":"μελεδαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μελεδαίνω</b></el> <el>(μελεδαίνω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μέλω'><el>μέλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to care for, be cumbered about</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to tend, attend to</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>γῆμαι οὐ μελεδαίνει</el> <i>cares</i> not to marry, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}